dationservice` 的延迟数据确实指向了它可能是根因的可能性。按照之前假设的验证任务及可见数据，支持假设。\n\n输出分析结果如下：\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"rrt\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"recommendationservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"During the anomaly period, the `rrt_max` increased from 12932.5 to 804041.0 and `rrt` increased from 4014.78 to 225851.24 for recommendationservice, both showing significant spikes compared to normal performance.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"The `rrt_max` change ratio was 1.9367 and the `rrt` change ratio was 1.9301, which were significantly higher than other services during the anomaly period.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
